ring_id: Left D3 Silver on Blue Band

comments: Hastings Pair. Fell from nest, taken to OWL, deployed telemetry on 28-Jul-2021, released a few days later.
Boundary Bay Airport Sibling Pair. Sibling to TERF13, nest fell down around Boundary Bay near airport, taken to OWL on June 01.
Formerly known as TEUS03. Bird recaptured, failed unit removed and replaced with new one.
Caught at Vancouver Landfill on 10 March 2022
